OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775016230
OL,3,CSNP pledge to open 'heart and lung
OL,4,CMOT' centres
OL,6,FAn SNP government elected in May would
OL,7,Fopen centres to provide "MOTs for lung
OL,8,Fand heart health", First Minister John
OL,9,FSwinney has said.
OL,11,FThe centres, which would open in
OL,12,Fcommunity settings including football
OL,13,Fstadiums, shopping centres and
OL,14,Fworkplaces, would be modelled on a
OL,15,FJapanese initiative.
OL,17,FScots would be screened for cancer,
OL,18,FCOPD and heart disease, the party
OL,19,Fsaid, in a bid to reduce the pressure
OL,20,Ffelt by the NHS.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
