FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775016230
OL,3,CSNP pledge to open 'heart and lung
OL,4,CMOT' centres
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of a visit to a
OL,7,Fpharmacy on Wednesday, SNP leader John
OL,8,FSwinney said: "The SNP will keep
OL,9,Fdriving progress in our NHS ` and that
OL,10,Fwill rely on innovation and putting an
OL,11,Feven greater focus on prevention.
OL,13,F"As our population ages and our
OL,14,Fhealthcare system faces growing
OL,15,Fpressure, proactive measures to keep
OL,16,Fpeople healthier are more important
OL,17,Fthan ever.
OL,26,@pD@OOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775016230
OL,3,CSNP pledge to open 'heart and lung
OL,4,CMOT' centres
OL,6,F"Our plans for new 'one-stop shops'
OL,7,Fwill provide MOTs for lung and heart
OL,8,Fhealth, making it quicker and easier
OL,9,Ffor people to access checks that could
OL,10,Fultimately save their lives.
OL,12,F"They will identify conditions
OL,13,Fearlier, improve outcomes and help
OL,14,Ffree up capacity in our NHS.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775016230
OL,3,CSNP pledge to open 'heart and lung
OL,4,CMOT' centres
OL,6,F"By bringing check-ups and advice into
OL,7,Feveryday community settings ` from
OL,8,Fworkplaces and pharmacies to football
OL,9,Fclubs and shopping centres ` we can
OL,10,Freach people who might not otherwise
OL,11,Fcome forward, particularly in more
OL,12,Fdisadvantaged communities where the
OL,13,Fburden of ill health is greatest."
OL,15,FScottish Lib Dem leader Alex Cole-
OL,16,FHamilton said the SNP "cannot be
OL,17,Ftrusted with your health".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@bO]xD@WOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775016230
OL,3,CSNP pledge to open 'heart and lung
OL,4,CMOT' centres
OL,6,F"The SNP are heading into this
OL,7,Felection with a series of broken
OL,8,Fpromises, so no-one will take any
OL,9,Ffresh pledges seriously," he said.
OL,11,F"They cannot be trusted with your
OL,12,Fhealth. They do not deserve a single
OL,13,Fvote from anyone who's struggling to
OL,14,Fget the vital care they need.
OL,16,F"After 19 years of uninterrupted SNP
OL,17,Ffailure on healthcare, Scotland
OL,18,Fdeserves change with fairness at its
OL,19,Fheart.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@YO]sD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775016230
OL,3,CSNP pledge to open 'heart and lung
OL,4,CMOT' centres
OL,6,F"Scottish Liberal Democrats are
OL,7,Fcommitted to delivering first-rate
OL,8,Fhealth care ` so you can see your GP,
OL,9,Fdentist or mental health professional
OL,10,Fwhen you need them. If you like the
OL,11,Fsound of that, you should back the
OL,12,FScottish Liberal Democrats on your
OL,13,Fsecond, peach regional ballot paper."
OL,15,FScottish Conservative health spokesman
OL,16,FSandesh Gulhane said the SNP cannot be
OL,17,Ftrusted to deliver on its promises
OL,18,Fregarding the NHS.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775016230
OL,3,CSNP pledge to open 'heart and lung
OL,4,CMOT' centres
OL,6,FHe said: "John Swinney has had two
OL,7,Fdecades to deliver for Scottish
OL,8,Fpatients but he's presiding over a
OL,9,Fpermanent crisis in our NHS.
OL,11,F"If this was such a good idea, he
OL,12,Fwouldn't have waited until an election
OL,13,Fperiod to announce it.
OL,15,F"The SNP cannot be trusted to deliver
OL,16,Fon their pledges in relation to
OL,17,FScotland's health service, considering
OL,18,Fthey've not met their pledge to
OL,19,Feradicate one-year waits for patients
OL,20,For their own cancer waiting-time
OL,21,Ftargets for a decade.
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775016230
OL,3,CSNP pledge to open 'heart and lung
OL,4,CMOT' centres
OL,6,F"Swinney will spend the next five
OL,7,Fyears obsessing over independence
OL,8,Frather than the NHS. That is why Scots
OL,9,Fmust use their peach ballot paper to
OL,10,Fvote Scottish Conservative wherever
OL,11,Fyou live in Scotland to stop an SNP
OL,12,Fmajority."
OL,14,FMr Swinney drew similar criticism from
OL,15,FScottish Labour, who said the NHS is
OL,16,Fnow "even worse" five years after the
OL,17,FSNP said it would recover the service.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@JO]xD@EOUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
