FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775016230
OL,3,CSNP pledge to open 'heart and lung
OL,4,CMOT' centres
OL,6,FScottish Labour health spokeswoman
OL,7,FDame Jackie Baillie said: "It takes a
OL,8,Fbrass neck for John Swinney to pretend
OL,9,Fhe's going to fix the mess he made of
OL,10,Four NHS.
OL,12,F"Five years ago the SNP promised to
OL,13,Fdeliver an NHS recovery and now things
OL,14,Fare even worse, so no-one is buying
OL,15,Fthis desperate spin.
OL,17,F"The truth is the John Swinney and the
OL,18,FSNP have been in government for nearly
OL,19,Ftwo decades ` if they knew how to
OL,20,Fimprove things, they would have done
OL,21,Fit by now.
OL,26,@oD@[OUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
