CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775016230
OL,3,CSNP pledge to open 'heart and lung
OL,4,CMOT' centres
OL,6,F"The only way to fix the crisis in our
OL,7,FNHS and give Scots the health service
OL,8,Fthey deserve is by voting Scottish
OL,9,FLabour on May 7, and getting rid of
OL,10,Fthis failing SNP government."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@]O]
